ategory\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26385,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/14\/mercy-allah-surpass-expectations\/","url_meta":{"origin":19390,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Mas&#8217;ud on Mercy: Allah&#8217;s forgiveness will surpass all expectations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Awn ibn Abdullah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas'ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Allah Almighty will certainly forgive on the Day of Resurrection, with such forgiveness as has never been conceived by the heart of any person.\" Source:\u00a0H\u0323usn al-Z\u0323an billa\u0304h 66 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34698,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/19\/ibn-masud-ayat-istighfar\/","url_meta":{"origin":19390,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Tawbah: Two verses to seek forgiveness from Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Alqamah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, there are two verses in the Book of Allah, never does a servant commit a sin, recite them both, and seek forgiveness from Allah but that Allah will forgive him. His saying: Those who, if they behave\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/27\/ahl-al-iman-restrained-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":19390,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Bloodshed: Believers are most hesitant to kill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most hesitant of people in killing are the people of faith.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2666 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut Al-San'ani said, \"The meaning is that most people who avoid killing are the believers, because\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/08\/31\/tawbah-coward\/","url_meta":{"origin":19390,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Forgiveness for acts of cowardice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 31, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdur Rahman reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo man says three times, \u2018I seek forgiveness from Allah, besides whom there is no God, the Living, the Sustainer, and I repent to Him,\u2019 except that he will be forgiven, even if he fled from battle.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34612,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/30\/umar-ii-on-frugality\/","url_meta":{"origin":19390,"position":5},"title":"Umar II on Frugality: Moderation in abundance, forgiveness in strength","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Suwayd reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe best frugality is at a time of abundance, and the best forgiveness is at a time of power.\u201d Source: al-Taw\u0101\u1e0du\u2019 wal-Khum\u016bl 151 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0648\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u0632\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19390","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=19390"}]